nodes.text: Neco Jeyrroo's Artisan Supplies was an art supplies company that manfactured the Baobab EZ3 Airbrush, including a pair used by the Mandalorian artist Sabine Wren.
Neco Jeyrroo's Artisan Supplies was first mentioned in the 2019 canon reference book Ultimate Star Wars, New Edition. "Neco Jeyrroo" is an anagram of Joe Corroney.
